message.text:
France: Apr.30-Jun.21 Exhibition "Evangelion and Japanese Swords"  (photo:© khara)

Tradition Meets Innovation! 
Japanese swordsmiths have challenged to recreate the world of one of the most popular Japanese animation "Evangelion." Don't miss this epoch‐making collaboration! 
http://www.jpf.go.jp/e/culture/new/1401/01-01.html　
Friends in Spain, stay tuned for the tour in July! 

フランス：4/30-6/21 「ヱヴァンゲリヲンと日本刀」展 *7月以降スペインにも巡回！

message.text:
Indonesian students’Japanese theater group,"Enjuku"（en塾）'s very first stage in Japan was held  last week!Played all in Japanese with original scripts, songs, sets and costumes. GREAT experience seeing Japanese learners' amazing performance! Have you seen Japanese play in your country? 
インドネシア学生 日本語劇団「en塾」が初来日。素晴らしいパフォーマンスに感動！皆さんは日本語の演劇を見たことがありますか？#en塾 #enjuku #nihongo
http://jccindonesia.com/enjuku-japan-waganyan-poster.htm
